autogen: autogen (configure generator)
autogen:
autogen: autogen generates program files from repetitive text with varied
autogen: substitutions.  Its goal is to simplify the maintenance of programs
autogen: that contain large amounts of repetitive text.  This is especially
autogen: valuable if there are several blocks of such text that must be kept
autogen: synchronized in parallel tables.
